entry.title: Special Weather Statement issued September 27 at 5:43AM EDT by NWS
entry.summary: ...Locally Dense Fog expected through 9 AM... Locally dense fog has developed along the Hudson and Mohawk Rivers, as well as smaller rivers, tributaries, swamps and wetlands throughout eastern New York and western New England. Parts of the thruway, northway, and interstate 88 will be affected by the locally dense fog.
